=head2 B<REQUIRED> TotalRequestCountMetric => ArrayRef[L<Paws::ApplicationSignals::MetricDataQuery>]

This structure defines the metric that is used as the "total requests"
number for a request-based SLO. The number observed for this metric is
divided by the number of "good requests" or "bad requests" that is
observed for the metric defined in C<MonitoredRequestCountMetric>.



